Structural Divergence Analysis

Maria Laura Marcos, Julian Echave

Introduction

In this case we studied the rrm family. We used as reference for the ENM the protein with pdb code 1fxla2. We simulated 10 mutants of this reference for each protein of the family. The rrm family is of the type alpha and beta and consists of the following proteins:

##  [8] "2msta"  "1hd1a"  "1fjeb1" "1iqta"  "1cvja1" "1cvja2" "2u1a"  
## [15] "1qm9a2" "1qm9a1" "1u2fa"  "1jmta"  "2u2f"
